    "text": "\u2022 \u201cSimplicity is the ultimate sophistication\u201d -Leonardo da Vinci . Based on a Japanese tea room, these clean lines and minimal lines make this build nothing you\u2019ve seen before. And I know this may look partly finished, but in fact it\u2019s 100% complete. Saul & Ayaka have really pushed the boundaries here and I believe it\u2019s paid off . Create the lifestyle you want and live it \u2022 \ud83d\ude90 2018 Mercedes Sprinter 4x4 144\u201d \ud83d\udcf8 @theryovan \ud83d\udccd New York, USA\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 \u2022 \ud83d\udcf2Follow @van_boy_life for more daily inspiring van life content\ud83e\udd19\ud83c\udffb \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 #mercedessprinter #sprinterconversion #builtnotbought #vanliving #vanconversion #alternativeliving #vanlife #vanlifediaries #vanlifeideas #campervan #projectvanlife #vanlifeexplorers #tinyhouse #homeiswhereyouparkit #homeonwheels #vanlove #vanlifers #adventuremobile #vanlifemovement #vanlifecommunity #vanbuild #vanlifegathering #vanlifesociety #campervan #vandweller #camperlife #vanlifestyle #outdoors #overland #camperconversion",
